{"tid":2099613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"否認以「雷射槍」射市民 警：使用的是「激光瞄準器」","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T13:35:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d5ddb19743f13a0007e23d92886680680ae3dd","tid":2099613,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"警方一直聲稱以「雷射槍」照射警員等同襲警，日前更有市民因此被判囚3個月。不過警方在上月9日於中環處理示威事件時，一名警員卻以長槍上配備的雷射槍，發出強勁綠色雷射光指向人群。警方回覆《蘋果》時拒絕解釋該支雷射槍是否常設裝備，但日前回覆灣仔區議員查詢時，就稱該支雷射槍是「激光瞄準器」，用以協助識別目標，但拒絕透露武器細節及使用指引。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/FAHAXROSB2BO2GPDVWLKYB5DYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FFAHAXROSB2BO2GPDVWLKYB5DYI%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=55b64f84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FFAHAXROSB2BO2GPDVWLKYB5DYI%2F&h=433c43e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/FAHAXROSB2BO2GPDVWLKYB5DYI/</a>"},{"pid":"ce92114a6af7bb4f08ac46337730dea950e6d9dc","tid":2099613,"uid":280056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"瞄準啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a91c50819f5773734dc78885c4aaa5c332ac727","tid":2099613,"uid":127735,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"否認以「汽油彈」掟警察，民：使用的是「火焰儲存器」"},{"pid":"ddae695d209da2c5bc5210dcc0b070e7bef85993","tid":2099613,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2a91c50819f5773734dc78885c4aaa5c332ac727","tid":2099613,"uid":127735,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"否認以「汽油彈」掟警察，民：使用的是「火焰儲存器」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"雞尾酒黎"},{"pid":"d189ca7515d514be43e01f30759a72edd990f5b3","tid":2099613,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl